                    <h3 class="fw-bold">Computer Science</h3>
                    <p  class="fw-bold fst-italic">Author: Dr. Alan Turing</p>
                    <p class="fst-italic">
                        Dive into the world of computer science with this comprehensive guide that covers fundamental concepts and modern advancements.
                        From algorithms and data structures to artificial intelligence and cybersecurity,
                        this book provides a solid foundation for beginners and a valuable resource for seasoned programmers.
                        Explore practical examples and hands-on exercises to enhance your understanding and skills in this ever-evolving field.
                        Perfect for students, educators, and tech enthusiasts looking to deepen their knowledge.</p>
                </div>
