                    <h3 class="fw-bold">Physics</h3>
                    <p class="fw-bold fst-italic">Author:Dr. James Maxwell</p>
                    <p class="fst-italic">
                        Description:
                        Explore the universe with this engaging introduction to physics. Covering core topics such as mechanics, thermodynamics, electromagnetism, and quantum physics,
                        this book provides a solid foundation for understanding the natural world. Rich with illustrations and practical examples, 
                        it helps demystify complex concepts and encourages critical thinking. Ideal for students, educators, and anyone curious about the laws that govern our universe.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="book-item">
                    <h3 class="fw-bold">English</h3>
                    <p class="fw-bold fst-italic">Author: Emily Clarke</p>
                    <p class="fst-italic">
                        Description:
                        Unlock the beauty of English literature with this insightful guide that explores classic and contemporary works. Delve into themes, literary devices, 
                        and critical analysis to enhance your appreciation and understanding of diverse genres.
                        Perfect for students, teachers, and literature enthusiasts seeking to deepen their literary knowledge and analytical skills.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="book-item">
                    <h3 class="fw-bold"> Essentials of Biology</h3>
                    <p class="fw-bold fst-italic">Author:Dr. Jane Goodall</p>
                    <p class="fst-italic">
                        Description:
                        Discover the wonders of life with this comprehensive guide to biology. Covering topics from cell biology to ecosystems, 
                        this book provides an in-depth look at the principles that govern living organisms. Rich with illustrations and real-world examples, 
                        it’s perfect for students, educators, and anyone fascinated by the natural world.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="book-item">
                    <h3 class="fw-bold">The Science Explorer</h3>
                    <p class="fw-bold fst-italic">Author: Dr. Carl Sagan</p>
                    <p class="fst-italic">
                        Description:
                        Embark on a journey through the fascinating realms of science with this engaging guide. 
                        Covering physics, chemistry, biology, and earth sciences, this book provides a comprehensive overview of key scientific principles.
                        Filled with vivid illustrations and practical examples, it’s perfect for students, educators,
                        and science enthusiasts eager to explore the mysteries of our universe
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="book-item">
                    <h3 class="fw-bold">The Art Appreciation Guide</h3>
                    <p class="fw-bold fst-italic">Author: Prof. Maria Sanchez</p>
                    <p class="fst-italic">
                        Description:
